# Secrets — NEVER commit signing certs / private keys (a code-signing .pfx was once
# committed and had to be purged from history; this keeps it from coming back).
*.pfx
*.p12
*.pem
*.key

# Rust build output
/target
/target-hero

# Locally built installers (wix build output) — both the CI `dist/` dir and the
# root-level MSI/PDB the website installer (`warbell.wxs`) emits during a release.
/dist/
/*.msi
/*.wixpdb
# Transient release notes the `/release` skill writes for the GitHub-release body.
/dist-notes.md

# Dev screenshots / comparison renders (the FOREST_SHOT harness writes PNGs here, and the
# per-biome reference shots live under shots/). Real game art lives under assets/.
/*.png
/shots/

# Promo / marketing captures (the FOREST_CLIP harness → ffmpeg renders GIFs/MP4s here).
/promo/

# Claude Code local runtime artifacts
/.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

/target-shot

# Playwright-MCP scratch output (console logs + page snapshots the browser tooling dumps).
/.playwright-mcp/

# Model-proportion pipeline intermediates — ~22 MB of generated depth sheets / contour PNGs /
# .npy the turnaround-extraction step writes (tools/ holds the scripts; the proportions are
# already baked into the Rust model builders, so these are dev-only derived artifacts).
/model_proportions/